# =============================================================================
# Jenkins Global Environment Variables Template
# =============================================================================
# File ini adalah TEMPLATE untuk environment variables di Jenkins.
#
# CARA SETUP:
# 1. Buka Jenkins: Manage Jenkins → Configure System
# 2. Scroll ke "Global properties"
# 3. Check "Environment variables"
# 4. Add setiap variable di bawah ini
#
# SECURITY WARNING:
# - JANGAN commit file ini dengan nilai asli ke repository
# - Gunakan nilai dummy/example di file ini
# - Set nilai asli HANYA di Jenkins Server
# =============================================================================

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# VPS Configuration
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# IP address atau hostname VPS target deployment
# Example: 202.155.90.93 atau vps.example.com
VPS_HOST=your_vps_ip_here

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Docker Registry Configuration
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Docker Hub username atau private registry
# Example: tlkmags
DOCKER_REGISTRY=your_docker_username

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Git Repository Configuration
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Full Git repository URL (HTTPS)
# Example: https://github.com/username/youtube-trennding-fetcher.git
GIT_REPO_URL=https://github.com/your_username/your_repo.git

# =============================================================================
# Jenkins Credentials (Setup via Credentials Manager)
# =============================================================================
# Credentials di bawah ini TIDAK di-set sebagai environment variables.
# Setup via: Manage Jenkins → Manage Credentials → Add Credentials
#
# 1. github-credentials (Username with password)
#    - Username: Your GitHub username
#    - Password: GitHub Personal Access Token
#    - Scope: repo (full control)
#
# 2. docker-hub-credentials (Username with password)
#    - Username: Your Docker Hub username
#    - Password: Docker Hub password or access token
#
# 3. vps-ssh-password (Username with password)
#    - Username: VPS SSH username (e.g., root, ubuntu)
#    - Password: VPS SSH password
#    - Alternative: Use SSH private key (more secure)
#
# 4. youtube-api-key (Secret text)
#    - Secret: Your YouTube Data API v3 key
#    - Get from: https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials
# =============================================================================

# =============================================================================
# VERIFICATION CHECKLIST
# =============================================================================
# Before running pipeline, verify:
# [ ] All 3 environment variables set in Jenkins
# [ ] All 4 credentials configured in Jenkins
# [ ] VPS_HOST is accessible from Jenkins server
# [ ] VPS port 8000 and 22 are open
# [ ] Docker Hub account is valid
# [ ] GitHub repository exists and accessible
# [ ] YouTube API key is valid and not quota exceeded
# =============================================================================
